  "title": "Accounts Executive",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p><ul><li>Daily bookkeeping, payments, and documentations</li><li>Handling full set of accounts which includes AR, AP, Inventory and GL</li><li>Assisting in monthly and yearly closing activities including reports and reconciliation</li><li>Preparing monthly and quarterly financial reports and accounts schedules</li><li>Preparing payment vouchers, journal entries and input into the system</li><li>Responsible for GST Submission</li><li>Liase with Auditors to coordinate the financial year end audit</li><li>Liase with Tax Consultant for providing accounts details for Income Tax Returns</li><li>Preparing of Survey and Statistics forms</li><li>Filing and documentation control</li><li>Any administrative duties or ad-hoc duties assigned from time to time</li></ul><p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 3 Year(s) full set of accounting experiences</li><li>Experiences in Construction field is preferred</li><li>Knowledge and hands - on experience in handling accounting software will be a plus</li><li>Good Knowledge of Microsoft Office applications</li><li>Possess initiative, good working attitude and have strong sense of responsibility</li><li>Team Player with ability to work independently</li></ul>",
